                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1" defective="false">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus/>According to the colophon, the Ms. was commissioned by ʾabba Zä-Krǝstos and written by the scribe Mälkǝʿa Krǝstos. It was completed in the year of Mathew, in 253 year of mercy (= 1601 A.D.), during the reign of King Yaʿqob (r. 1597-1603, 1605-07) and tenure of Metropolitan Ṗeṭros (1599?-1606).</colophon>
